82
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:03,890
into an inhomogenous ones.

83
00:06:03,890 --> 00:06:05,372
For electromagnetic interactions,

84
00:06:05,372 --> 00:06:08,659
the inhomogeneous equation is derived
from the Klein-Gordon equation by the so-called

85
00:06:08,659 --> 00:06:11,760
minimal substitution. To struct this
