the polarization of particles

178
00:13:06,290 --> 00:13:10,950
in the final state either, one must
sum the cross-section corresponding

179
00:13:10,950 --> 00:13:13,930
to the spin direction of
the final state particles.

180
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:19,290
The square of the amplitude resulting from
both operations,

181
00:13:19,290 --> 00:13:23,920
averaging over initial spin and
summing over final spin,

182
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:28,870
